Kau bisu?

7
00:00:26,081 --> 00:00:29,668
Kenapa kau sembunyi
di gudang kimchi Kapten Ri?

8
00:00:30,252 --> 00:00:31,169
Lupakan.

9
00:00:31,586 --> 00:00:34,631
Bahkan orang bisu bisa bicara
saat mereka ke Badan Keamanan.

10
00:00:38,468 --> 00:00:39,719
- Astaga.
